<reg_short_dscr>:
QSGMII Status Register
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
QSGMII Receive Status Register
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Set when QSGMII channel has successfully synchronized on K28.1 code-group, this field is only valid when PORT_CONF:QSGMII_CFG_STAT:QSGMII_CFG.SHYST_DIS is 0.
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Synchronization status of connected ports.
Each bit is indicated the status of a port, LSB is port 0 up to MSB for port 3
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0 :  out of sync
1 :  in sync
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Variable RX Bit Delay from barrel shifter
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
delay is calculeted as  N x 200ps  with N=[0;39]
------------------------------
