<reg_short_dscr>:
USGMII Status Register
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
USGMII status register
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Indicates if USGMII has successfully synchronized on K28.1 code-group (shyst_dis must be cleared)
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0: USGMII is out of sync
1: USGMII has synchronized
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Synchronization status of connected ports.
Each bit is indicated the status of a port, LSB is port 0 up to MSB for port 7.
In QSGMII mode only bits 0 to 3 are valid.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0 :  out of sync
1 :  in sync
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Variable RX Bit Delay from barrel shifter
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
delay is calculeted as  N x 200ps  with N=[0;39]
